lore: §7The Skeleton is a mob that spawns naturally in the
§7Diamond Reserve and Obsidian Sanctuary of the
§7Deep Caverns, as well as on the Player's Private
§7Island at night. Additionally, they can be found at
§7the Gravel Ravine in the Spider's Den, in the High
§7Level area, or spawned by a Skeleton Minion.
